main event: Sighting reported as unidentified on October 26, 1964, in Summit, New Jersey.
interesting points: The case was marked as unreleaseable and no object was actually observed by witnesses., The report is the initial and only record of this incident., A request for PID Form 164 was made with negative results., There is a noted 90-day delay in sightings in the vicinity of Summit, N.J., Correspondence with Project Blue Book regarding this sighting has been ongoing since before this incident.
witness description: No witnesses confirmed the observation of any objects.
